      <title>俄羅斯安加拉火箭週四進行第三次發射嘗試</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/third-launch-try-russias-angara-rocket-thursday-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄羅斯將於週四開始第三次嘗試進行安加拉-A5太空火箭的試射，此前技術故障導致官員連續兩天在最後一刻中止任務。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/third-launch-try-russias-angara-rocket-thursday-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:57:17 GMT</pubDate>
